As more people clicked on those links and read my articles, I started to get noticed by other editors who were interested in learning more about Fulani culture. They would leave comments on my articles and even start editing them themselves, which helped me build credibility within the community. Eventually, I was able to earn enough reputation points to unlock new features and tools that allowed me to create even more content and attract even more readers.
